nt-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">হবে। </span></span></span></span></p>\r\nঅর্থাৎ If clause টি তে were থাকলে পরের clause এ subject+would/could/might+ verb এর base form(v1)+ extension হবে। \r\n\r\nExample: If I were you, I wouldn’t tell anyone about this.	0	88	2021-01-31 03:41:20.767117+00
