428	<p><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">He never came again, ______? Add a question tag to this sentence.</span></span></p>\r\n	1700	<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">The adverbs&nbsp;never,&nbsp;rarely,&nbsp;seldom,&nbsp;hardly,&nbsp;barely&nbsp;and&nbsp;scarcely&nbsp;have a negative sense. Even though they may be in a positive statement, the feeling of the statement is negative. We treat statements with these words like negative statements, so the question tag is normally positive.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	0	85	2021-01-29 18:39:00.557051+00
