ze:16.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">দিলে</span></span> <span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">১ ঘন্টায়</span></span> <span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">পূর্ণ হয় চৌবাচ্চাটির = ১/১০+১/১২+১/১৫ অংশ</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; =[৬+৫+৪]/৬০&nbsp; &ldquo;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; =১৫/৬০&nbsp; &ldquo;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; =১/৪&nbsp; &ldquo;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">১/৪ অংশ পূর্ণ হয় ১ ঘন্টায়</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">১&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &ldquo;&nbsp;&nbsp; &ldquo;&nbsp; &ldquo; = ১ </span></span><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">&times; ৪/১ </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">= ৪ ঘন্টায় </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">তিনটি</span></span> <span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">নল</span></span> <span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">একসঙ্গে</span></span> <span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">খুলে</span></span> <span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">দিলে</span></span> <span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">চৌবাচ্চাটি</span></span> <span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">পূর্ণ</span></span> <span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">হতে</span></span> <span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">৪ ঘন্টা</span></span> <span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">সময়</span></span> <span style="font-size: