402	<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">৬ জন লোক ও ৮ জন বালক একটি কাজ ১০ দিনে শেষ করতে পারে। যদি ঐ একই কাজ ২৬ জন লোক ও ৪৮ জন বালক ২ দিনে শেষ করতে পারে তাহলে ১৫ জন লোক ও ২০ জন বালক ঐ কাজ কত দিনে শেষ করবে</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">?</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	1595	<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">প্রশ্নমতে</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">, (</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">৬ জন লোক+৮ জন বালক)</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">&times;</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">১০ = (২৬ জন লোক+৪৮ জন বালক)</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">&times;2</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">&nbsp; &nbsp; বা</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">, </span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">৩০ জন লোক + ৪০ জন বালক = ২৬ জন লোক + ৪৮ জন বালক</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">বা</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">, </span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">৪ জন লোক = ৮ জন বালক </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">অর্থা</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:&quot;Nirmala UI&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">ৎ</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">, </span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">১ জন লোক ২ জন বালকের সমান কাজ করতে পারে৷</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">৬জন লোক= ১২ জন বালক</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">১২+৮ = ২০ জন বালক ১ টি কাজ করে ১০ দিনে</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">তাহলে ১ জন বালক কাজটি করবে ২০</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">&times;</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">১০ = ২০০ দিনে</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">তাহলে</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">, </span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">১৫ জন লোক =১৫</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">&times;</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">২ = ৩০ জন বালক </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">৩০+২০= ৫০ জন বালক কাজটি করতে পারে <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mstyle mathsize="14px"><mfrac><mrow><mi>&#2536;</mi><mi>&#2534;</mi><mi>&#2534;</mi></mrow><mi>&#2538;</mi></mfrac></mstyle></math> </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Vrinda"><span style="color:black">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= ৪ দিনে৷</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	0	85	2021-01-29 17:14:44.62748+00
