394	<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Nasim said to the boy, &quot;Will you come with me?&quot; Change the speech.</span></span></span></span></p>	1564	<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:#201f1e">Interrogative Sentence কে Direct থেকে Indirect Narration এ পরিবর্তন করার নিয়ম-</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:#201f1e">১</span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:#201f1e">. Reporting verb টি ask, demand of, enquire of, want to know, wonder এ পরিবর্তন হয়</span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:#201f1e">।</span></span></span> </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:#201f1e">২</span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:#201f1e">. Reported speech টি যদি Auxiliary verb দ্বারা শুরু হয় তাহলে linker হিসেবে if/ whether বসবে</span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:#201f1e">।</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:#201f1e">৩</span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:#201f1e">. Reported speech এর অন্তর্গত Interrogative Sentence টি যদি কোনো Wh- question word দ্বারা শুরু হয়, তাহলে তা অপরিবর্তিত থাকবে অর্থা</span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Nirmala UI&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:#201f1e">ৎ</span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:#201f1e"> সেই</span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:#201f1e"> Wh- question word টিই বসবে</span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:#201f1e">।</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:#201f1e">৪</span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:#201f1e">. Direct speech এর Interrogative Sentence টি Indirect এ Assertive Sentence এ পরিবর্তত হয়</span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:#201f1e">।</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:#201f1e">Example:</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:#201f1e">Direct: </span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Nasim said to the boy, &quot;Will you come with me?&quot;</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:#201f1e">Indirect: </span></span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:black">Nasim asked the boy if she would go with him.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>	0	85	2021-01-29 16:22:29.902069+00
