493	<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">It is time (do) the work</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	1962	<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">উপরের </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">Fill in the blank </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">এ </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">to do </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">বসবে। কেননা </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">Sentence </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">এ </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">It is time, It is high time </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">ইত্যাদির পরে </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">Subject </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">থাকলে </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">Subject </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">এর পর </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">Verb </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">এর পর </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">Past Form </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">হয়। </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">Subject </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">না থাকলে </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">to+verb </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">এর </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">Present Form </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">হয়। সাধারণত কোনো কিছু করার সময় হয়েছে অর্থে </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">It is time </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">ব্যবহৃত হয়।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">অপরপক্ষে</span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">, </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">যা পূর্বেই করা দরকার ছিল</span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">, </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">যা করতে দেরি হয়ে গেছে অর্থা</span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Nirmala UI&quot;,sans-serif">ৎ</span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif"> যা করার এখনই উপযুক্ত সময় অর্থে </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">It is high time </span></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">ব্যবহৃত হয়।</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Vrinda&quot;,sans-serif">Example: It is high time he changed his bad habits.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n	0	88	2021-01-31 03:53:46.81607+00
